{"tid":818142,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【🌋樓爆2018】😭新盤銷情慘淡只收5800票！淡淡宜等跌八成","createTime":"2018-09-14T01:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T03:05:00.000Z","uid":43146,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1c8c9bd23dc45c843f7f40c24c286be293cf0b6b","tid":818142,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T01:57:52.000Z","msg":"【堆填區新盤】康城LP6今截票累收逾5800票 超額10.8倍<br />\n12小時前6.2K<br />\n即時財經<br />\n <br />\nLP6今截票累收5800票，超額10.8倍。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n由南豐集團發展的日出康城LP6，本周六再度賣488伙單位，項目今晚截止登記，發展商稱，項目收票逾5,800張，超額認購近10.8倍。<br />\n<br />\n於本周六發售的推488伙，實用面積307至1086方呎，1房至4房間隔，以定價計，售價556.3萬至2281.9萬元，買家可享最高19.5%折扣，折實售價447.9萬至1837萬元，呎價13029至18697元，折實均價15,541。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全球樓行 Dream House零距離<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&d=AAikRAnnkpmqLFbgyV%2BMLI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=63c762d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&h=9bc132df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty</a>"},{"pid":"9d92236970ee805a55a75b0a40ad9af48207aacd","tid":818142,"uid":35408,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:09:34.000Z","msg":"超額10倍叫慘淡? 我dllm"},{"pid":"b39c6b29535adbeeaa9df1cb38cfa214320a67a9","tid":818142,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:09:35.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430f86bae85da6101324b6de87ddfd685e5a654c","tid":818142,"uid":43146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d92236970ee805a55a75b0a40ad9af48207aacd","tid":818142,"uid":35408,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:09:34.000Z","msg":"超額10倍叫慘淡? 我dllm"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:10:15.000Z","msg":"黎緊應該大跌<br />\n買個班人即變負資產等call loan"},{"pid":"6